    "note": "Vinland Saga's manga concluded with chapter 220 on July 25, 2025, after 20 years of serialization. 29 tankōbon volumes. The anime has adapted 48 episodes covering only the War Arc (ch 1–54) and Slave Arc (ch 55–99). The Eastern Expedition Arc (ch 100–166) and Vinland Arc (ch 167–220) are unadapted. No Season 3 has been announced as of March 2026."
  },
